marketing:
Shell Omala S2 A 320 is a high performance gear lubricant for enclosed industrial gears including worm gears. Shell Omala S2 A 320 is formulated to provide excellent lubrication, stability and extend service life. 
Shell Omala S2 A 320 is anhydrous and does not readily hydrolyze in the presence of water.  It is designed to resist the formation of sludge and varnish.
